sql.up: CREATE TABLE web_pages (id text NOT NULL DEFAULT 'page_'::text || xata_private.xid()::text, doc_id text NOT NULL, title text NOT NULL, description text, favicon text, banner text, link text NOT NULL, text text, xata_version int NOT NULL DEFAULT 0, xata_createdat timestamptz(6) NOT NULL DEFAULT current_timestamp, xata_updatedat timestamptz(6) NOT NULL DEFAULT current_timestamp, xata_id text NOT NULL DEFAULT 'rec_'::text || xata_private.xid()::text, CONSTRAINT web_pages_pkey PRIMARY KEY (id))
